      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 1:14">Hes 1:14</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 2:14">2:14</ref></char>
    </note> Siku ya sita Eliasafu mwana wa Deueli, mkuu wa wana wa Gadi <verse eid="NUM 7:42" /><verse number="43" style="v" sid="NUM 7:43" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:43 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 2:5">Law 2:5</ref>; <ref loc="LEV 14:10">14:10</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 1:9">Ebr 1:9</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 2:27">1 Yoh 2:27</ref></char></note> matoleo yake yalikuwa sahani moja ya fedha, uzani wake ni shekeli mia moja na thelathini, na bakuli moja ya fedha, uzani wake shekeli sabini, kwa shekeli ya mahali patakatifu; vyombo hivyo vyote viwili vilikuwa vimejaa unga mwembamba uliochanganywa na mafuta, kuwa sadaka ya unga; <verse eid="NUM 7:43" /><verse number="44" style="v" sid="NUM 7:44" />na kijiko kimoja cha dhahabu, uzani wake shekeli kumi, kilichojaa uvumba; <verse eid="NUM 7:44" /><verse number="45" style="v" sid="NUM 7:45" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:45 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 40:6">Zab 40:6</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 51:16">51:16</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 1:11">Isa 1:11</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 53:4">53:4</ref>; <ref loc="JER 7:22">Yer 7:22</ref>; <ref loc="AMO 5:22">Amo 5:22</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 5:21">2 Kor 5:21</ref></char></note> na ng'ombe dume mchanga mmoja, na kondoo dume mmoja, na mwana-kondoo dume mmoja wa mwaka mmoja, kuwa sadaka ya kuteketezwa; <verse eid="NUM 7:45" /><verse number="46" style="v" sid="NUM 7:46" />na mbuzi dume mmoja kwa sadaka ya dhambi; <verse eid="NUM 7:46" /><verse number="47" style="v" sid="NUM 7:47" />tena kwa ajili ya dhabihu ya sadaka za amani, ng'ombe dume wawili, na kondoo dume watano, na mbuzi dume watano, na wana-kondoo dume watano wa mwaka mmoja; hayo ndiyo matoleo ya Eliasafu mwana wa Deueli.<verse eid="NUM 7:47" /></para>
