      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 1:10">Hes 1:10</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 2:20">2:20</ref></char>
    </note> Siku ya nane Gamalieli mwana wa Pedasuri, mkuu wa wana wa Manase; <verse eid="NUM 7:54" /><verse number="55" style="v" sid="NUM 7:55" />matoleo yake yalikuwa sahani moja ya fedha, uzani wake ni shekeli mia moja na thelathini, na bakuli moja ya fedha, uzani wake shekeli sabini, kwa shekeli ya mahali patakatifu; vyombo hivyo vyote viwili vilikuwa vimejaa unga mwembamba uliochanganywa na mafuta, kuwa sadaka ya unga; <verse eid="NUM 7:55" /><verse number="56" style="v" sid="NUM 7:56" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:56 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 30:7">Kut 30:7</ref></char></note> na kijiko kimoja cha dhahabu, uzani wake shekeli kumi, kilichojaa uvumba; <verse eid="NUM 7:56" /><verse number="57" style="v" sid="NUM 7:57" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:57 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 12:5">Kut 12:5</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 1:29">Yn 1:29</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 8:32">Mdo 8:32</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 1:19">1 Pet 1:19</ref>; <ref loc="REV 5:6">Ufu 5:6</ref></char></note> na ng'ombe dume mchanga mmoja, na kondoo dume mmoja, na mwana-kondoo dume mmoja wa mwaka mmoja, kuwa sadaka ya kuteketezwa; <verse eid="NUM 7:57" /><verse number="58" style="v" sid="NUM 7:58" />na mbuzi dume mmoja kwa sadaka ya dhambi; <verse eid="NUM 7:58" /><verse number="59" style="v" sid="NUM 7:59" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:59 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 3:1">Law 3:1</ref>; <ref loc="MIC 5:5">Mik 5:5</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 5:19">2 Kor 5:19</ref>,<ref loc="2CO 5:21">21</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 2:14">Efe 2:14</ref></char></note> tena kwa ajili ya dhabihu ya sadaka za amani, ng'ombe dume wawili, na kondoo dume watano, na mbuzi dume watano, na wana-kondoo dume watano wa mwaka mmoja; hayo ndiyo matoleo ya Gamalieli mwana wa Pedasuri.<verse eid="NUM 7:59" /></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="60" style="v" sid="NUM 7:60" />Siku ya tisa Abidani mwana wa Gideoni, mkuu wa wana wa Benyamini; <verse eid="NUM 7:60" /><verse number="61" style="v" sid="NUM 7:61" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:61 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 1:11">Hes 1:11</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 2:22">2:22</ref></char></note> matoleo yake yalikuwa sahani moja ya fedha, uzani wake ni shekeli mia moja na thelathini, na bakuli moja ya fedha, uzani wake shekeli sabini, kwa shekeli ya mahali patakatifu; vyombo hivyo vyote viwili vilikuwa vimejaa unga mwembamba uliochanganywa na mafuta, kuwa sadaka ya unga; <verse eid="NUM 7:61" /><verse number="62" style="v" sid="NUM 7:62" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:62 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 66:20">Isa 66:20</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 141:2">Zab 141:2</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 9:27">Dan 9:27</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 15:16">Rum 15:16</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 4:18">Flp 4:18</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 13:15">Ebr 13:15</ref>; <ref loc="REV 5:8">Ufu 5:8</ref>; <ref loc="REV 8:3">8:3</ref>,<ref loc="REV 8:4">4</ref></char></note> na kijiko kimoja cha dhahabu, uzani wake shekeli kumi, kilichojaa uvumba; <verse eid="NUM 7:62" /><verse number="63" style="v" sid="NUM 7:63" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:63 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 40:6">Zab 40:6</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 53:4">Isa 53:4</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 5:21">2 Kor 5:21</ref></char></note> na ng'ombe dume mchanga mmoja, na kondoo dume mmoja, na mwana-kondoo dume mmoja wa mwaka mmoja, kuwa sadaka ya kuteketezwa; <verse eid="NUM 7:63" /><verse number="64" style="v" sid="NUM 7:64" />na mbuzi dume mmoja kwa sadaka ya dhambi; <verse eid="NUM 7:64" /><verse number="65" style="v" sid="NUM 7:65" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:65 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 3:1">Law 3:1</ref>; <ref loc="1KI 8:63">1 Fal 8:63</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 7:14">Mit 7:14</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 45:17">Eze 45:17</ref>; <ref loc="COL 1:20">Kol 1:20</ref></char></note> tena kwa ajili ya dhabihu ya sadaka za amani, ng'ombe dume wawili, na kondoo dume watano, na mbuzi dume watano, na wana-kondoo dume watano wa mwaka mmoja; hayo ndiyo matoleo ya Abidani mwana wa Gideoni.<verse eid="NUM 7:65" /></para>
