    </note> Siku ya kumi Ahiezeri mwana wa Amishadai, mkuu wa wana wa Dani; <verse eid="NUM 7:66" /><verse number="67" style="v" sid="NUM 7:67" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:67 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 27:25">Law 27:25</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 3:47">Hes 3:47</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 30:13">Kut 30:13</ref></char></note> matoleo yake yalikuwa sahani moja ya fedha, uzani wake ni shekeli mia moja na thelathini, na bakuli moja ya fedha, uzani wake shekeli sabini, kwa shekeli ya mahali patakatifu; vyombo hivyo vyote viwili vilikuwa vimejaa unga mwembamba uliochanganywa na mafuta, kuwa sadaka ya unga; <verse eid="NUM 7:67" /><verse number="68" style="v" sid="NUM 7:68" /><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:68 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 30:7-9">Kut 30:7-9</ref>; <ref loc="NUM 16:35">Hes 16:35</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 141:2">Zab 141:2</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 66:20">Isa 66:20</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 9:27">Dan 9:27</ref>; <ref loc="MAL 1:11">Mal 1:11</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 1:9">Lk 1:9</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 15:16">Rum 15:16</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 4:18">Flp 4:18</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 13:15">Ebr 13:15</ref></char></note> na kijiko kimoja cha dhahabu, uzani wake shekeli kumi, kilichojaa uvumba; <verse eid="NUM 7:68" /><verse number="69" style="v" sid="NUM 7:69" />na ng'ombe dume mchanga mmoja, na kondoo dume mmoja, na mwana-kondoo dume mmoja wa mwaka mmoja, kuwa sadaka ya kuteketezwa; <verse eid="NUM 7:69" /><verse number="70" style="v" sid="NUM 7:70" />na mbuzi dume mmoja kwa sadaka ya dhambi; <verse eid="NUM 7:70" /><verse number="71" style="v" sid="NUM 7:71" />tena kwa ajili ya dhabihu ya sadaka za amani, ng'ombe dume wawili, na kondoo dume watano, na mbuzi dume watano, na wana-kondoo dume watano wa mwaka mmoja; hayo ndiyo matoleo ya Ahiezeri mwana wa Amishadai.<verse eid="NUM 7:71" /></para>
